Revision history for Minions

{{$NEXT}}

0.000008 2016-01-16T14:37:46Z
        - Corrects test failures in Perl 5.12.x and earlier.
        - The $__foo syntax is deprecated in favour of $FOO

0.000007 2016-01-10T19:20:19Z
        - Documentation updates.
        - reader => 1 and writer => 1 are no longer supported (their meaning was not obvious)
        - Simpler syntax for calling semiprivate methods.
        - Added option to allow $self->{$ATTR} syntax.
        - Migrated to Minilla.

0.000006  2015-01-22 21:54:21 GMT
        - Documentation updates.

0.000005  2015-01-21 22:33:37 GMT
        - More automation for implementations.
        - More documentation added.

0.000004  2014-12-12 21:09:49 GMT
        - Test CPAN indexing. No changes.

0.000003  2014-12-12 19:40:29 GMT
        - Expanded docs. Renamed project (was Class::Minion).

0.000002  2014-11-19 14:16:36 GMT
        - Initial release
